notes.title: Short Story
notes.content: Once, there was a man who was extremely forgetful. One day, he decided to go to the bank to withdraw some money. As he was filling out the withdrawal slip, he forgot his account number, so he turned to the person standing behind him and asked, "Excuse me, do you know my account number?"

notes.title: Dooms Day
notes.content: Doomsday, also known as the end of the world, refers to a hypothetical event where all life on Earth comes to an end. The idea of doomsday has been a common theme in religion, mythology, and popular culture. While there have been various predictions and theories about the end of the world, no such event has occurred so far.
